      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the firm, the funding, the house... all of it. i just lost the last of the bridge loan today. i don't even know how to tell my parents. they worked their whole lives so i could do this and now i've just dragged the family name through the dirt. i feel like a walking disaster. i can't face them. i can't face anyone.",
